    {
      "id": "23-s0736",
      "originalId": "s0736",
      "blockIndex": 23,
      "chinese": "王與伯升首舉義兵，更始因其資以據帝位，而不能奉承大統，敗亂綱紀，盜賊日多，羣生危蹙。",
      "literal": "The king and Bosheng first raised righteous troops, Gengshi relied on their resources to take the imperial position, but could not uphold the great lineage, defeated and disordered the fundamental principles, bandits daily increased, the common people in danger and distress.",
      "idiomatic": "You and Bosheng were the first to raise the banner of righteous rebellion. Gengshi relied on your resources to seize the imperial throne, but he could not uphold the great imperial legacy. He has thrown the fundamental principles into chaos, allowed bandits to multiply daily, and plunged all living beings into danger and distress."
    },
    {
      "id": "23-s0737",
      "originalId": "s0737",
      "blockIndex": 23,
      "chinese": "〈蹙，迫也，音子六反。",
