      "idiomatic": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "23-s0739",
      "originalId": "s0739",
      "blockIndex": 23,
      "chinese": "大王初征昆陽，王莽自潰；",
      "literal": "",
      "idiomatic": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "23-s0740",
      "originalId": "s0740",
      "blockIndex": 23,
      "chinese": "後拔邯鄲，北州弭定；",
      "literal": "",
      "idiomatic": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "23-s0741",
      "originalId": "s0741",
      "blockIndex": 23,
      "chinese": "參分天下而有其二，跨州據土，帶甲百萬。",
      "literal": "",
      "idiomatic": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "23-s0742",
      "originalId": "s0742",
      "blockIndex": 23,
      "chinese": "言武力則莫之敢抗，論文德則無所與辭。",
