    },
    {
      "id": "23-s0743",
      "originalId": "s0743",
      "blockIndex": 23,
      "chinese": "臣聞帝王不可以乆曠，天命不可以謙拒，惟大王以社稷為計，萬姓為心。",
      "literal": "",
      "idiomatic": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "23-s0744",
      "originalId": "s0744",
      "blockIndex": 23,
      "chinese": "」光武又不聽。",
      "literal": "",
      "idiomatic": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "24-s0745",
